'''Skip 6''' was an [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] located in the same [[Asteroid field/Legends|asteroid belt]] as the infamous [[Smuggler's Run/Legends|Smuggler's Run]]. It was used as a headquarters for the [[Glottalphib]] crime boss known as [[Nandreeson]]. He chose to fill the caves with pools of water filled with algae, in order to make the asteroid more comfortable to his fellow Glottalphibs.

